           title="Cherryleaf Blog"
           xmlUrl="https://www.cherryleaf.com/blog/feed/"
           type="rss"
           htmlUrl="https://www.cherryleaf.com/blog/"
           description="Blog from UK-based technical communication consultancy Cherryleaf covering a wide range of topics including content strategy, documentation tools, tech comm careers, and emerging trends like AI.">
  </outline>
  
