           type="rss"
           htmlUrl="https://clickhelp.com/clickhelp-technical-writing-blog"
           description="Blog maintained by ClickHelp (a SaaS platform for topic-based help) covering industry news, how-to articles, general best practices, and occasional product announcements relevant to technical writers.">
  </outline>
  
