           htmlUrl="https://jamestasse.tech/blog"
           description="Mostly covering the involvement of AI in technical writing, James takes a highly technical and analytical approach to tooling and content.">
  </outline>
  
  <outline text="Just Write Click"
           title="Just Write Click"
           xmlUrl="https://justwriteclick.com/feed"
           type="rss"
           htmlUrl="https://justwriteclick.com"
           description="Anne Gentle’s blog (author of *Docs Like Code*) about treating docs like code.Covers continuous publishing, static site generators (Sphinx, Hugo, etc), open-source documentation collaboration, and innovative content strategy techniques for technical writing teams.">
  </outline>
  
  <outline text="Kevin R. Kuhl"
           title="Kevin R. Kuhl"
